  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to follow tumoral proteins metabolism by in vivo no radioactive
      isotopic tagging (carbon 13 and nitrogen 15).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The project aims to study protein turnover in glioblastoma using mass spectrometry after
      13C-valine incorporation. This will allow to identify proteins in circulation secreted by
      tumor which could be diagnostic and pronostic biomarkers in patients With High-grade Glioma.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
